We ask your consent to add your anonymized responses to the growing dataset of teaming data. Your choice to participate in the research or not WILL NOT AFFECT  your ability to finish class assignments, receive feedback from these assessments, or your grade in the class. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact Sara Beckman (beckman@berkeley.edu).
